trans-unit.source: Extends the design mode behavior of a component.
trans-unit.target: Utvider utformingen modus virkemåten for en komponent.

trans-unit.source: The ComponentDesigner base designer class provides a simple designer that can extend the behavior of an associated component in design mode.
trans-unit.target: ComponentDesigner designer basisklassen gir en enkel designer som kan utvide virkemåten til den tilknyttede komponenten i utformingsmodus.

trans-unit.source: ComponentDesigner provides an empty <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerFilter> interface implementation, whose methods can be overridden to adjust the attributes, properties and events of the associated component at design time.
trans-unit.target: ComponentDesigner gir et tomt <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerFilter>grensesnitt implementering, der metoder kan overstyres til å justere attributter, egenskaper og hendelser for den tilknyttede komponenten under utformingen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerFilter>

trans-unit.source: You can associate a designer with a type using a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignerAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan knytte en designer til en type med en <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignerAttribute>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignerAttribute>

trans-unit.source: For an overview of customizing design-time behavior, see [Extending Design-Time Support](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For en oversikt over tilpasse utformingen virkemåte, kan du se [utvider støtte for utforming](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The ComponentDesigner class implements a special behavior for the property descriptors of inherited components.
trans-unit.target: ComponentDesigner klassen implementerer spesielle virkemåte for egenskapen beskrivelser av arvede komponentene.

trans-unit.source: An internal type named `InheritedPropertyDescriptor` is used by the default ComponentDesigner implementation to stand in for properties that are inherited from a base class.
trans-unit.target: En intern type navnet `InheritedPropertyDescriptor` brukes av standard ComponentDesigner implementering kan stå i for egenskaper som er arvet fra en basisklasse.

trans-unit.source: There are two cases in which these property descriptors are added.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes to tilfeller disse egenskapen beskrivelser er lagt til.

trans-unit.source: To the root object itself, which is returned by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost.RootComponent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property, because you are inheriting from its base class.
trans-unit.target: Til rotobjekt seg selv som returneres av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost.RootComponent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen fordi du arving fra den grunnleggende klasse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost.RootComponent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To fields found in the base class of the root object.
trans-unit.target: Til felt i basisklassen for root-objektet.

trans-unit.source: Public and protected fields from the base class are added to the designer so that they can be manipulated by the user.
trans-unit.target: Offentlige og beskyttet felt fra basisklassen er lagt til i designer slik at de kan redigeres av brukeren.

trans-unit.source: The `InheritedPropertyDescriptor` class modifies the default value of a property, so that the default value is the current value at object instantiation.
trans-unit.target: Den `InheritedPropertyDescriptor` klassen endrer standardverdien for en egenskap, slik at standardverdien er den gjeldende verdien på instantiering av objektet.

trans-unit.source: This is because the property is inherited from another instance.
trans-unit.target: Dette er fordi egenskapen er arvet fra en annen forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The designer defines resetting the property value as setting it to the value that was set by the inherited class.
trans-unit.target: Designer definerer tilbakestille egenskapsverdien som konfigurasjonen til verdien som er angitt av arvede klassen.

trans-unit.source: This value may differ from the default value stored in metadata.
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien kan være forskjellig fra verdien som er lagret i metadataene.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the design-time action lists supported by the component associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter listene utformingen handlingen støttes av komponenten som er forbundet med designer.

trans-unit.source: The design-time action lists supported by the component associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Listene utformingen handlingen støttes av komponenten som er forbundet med designer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of components associated with the component managed by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter komponenter som er knyttet til komponenten administreres av designer-samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This property indicates any components to copy or move along with the component managed by the designer during a copy, drag, or move operation.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir komponenter å kopiere eller flytte sammen med komponenten administreres av designer under en kopi dra, eller Flytt operasjonen.

trans-unit.source: If this collection contains references to other components in the current design mode document, those components will be copied along with the component managed by the designer during a copy operation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne samlingen inneholder referanser til andre komponenter i det gjeldende utformingen modus dokumentet, kopieres disse komponentene sammen med komponenten administreres av designer under en kopieringen.

trans-unit.source: When the component managed by the designer is selected, this collection is filled with any nested controls.
trans-unit.target: Når komponenten administrert av designeren er valgt, er denne samlingen fylt med nestede kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This collection can also include other components, such as the buttons of a toolbar.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen kan også inkludere andre komponenter, for eksempel knappene i verktøylinje.

trans-unit.source: The components that are associated with the component managed by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Komponentene som er knyttet til komponenten administreres av utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the component this designer is designing.
trans-unit.target: Henter komponenten utformeren utformer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A> method of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> sets this property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A>-metoden til <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>, settes denne egenskapen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When overriding the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A> method, be sure to call the base class <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A> method before using this property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når overstyrer den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A>metoden, må du huske å kalle basisklassen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A>metoden før du bruker denne egenskapen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The component managed by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Komponenten administreres av utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A> when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Kall <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>Når du er ferdig med <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A> method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>metoden forlater den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>ble bruker.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A> before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Ring alltid <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref> og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()` metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>referanser.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Creates a method signature in the source code file for the default event on the component and navigates the user's cursor to that location.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en metodesignatur i koden kildefilen for standardhendelsen på komponenten og navigerer markøren til denne plasseringen.

trans-unit.source: In Windows Forms and Web Forms designers, this method is invoked when a user double-clicks a component.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er i Windows Forms og webskjema utviklere aktiveres når en bruker dobbeltklikker en komponent.

trans-unit.source: An attempt to check out a file that is checked into a source code management program failed.
trans-unit.target: Et forsøk på å sjekke ut en fil som blir sjekket inn et program for behandling mislyktes.

trans-unit.source: Attempts to free resources by calling <xref uid="langword_csharp_Dispose(false)" name="Dispose(false)" href=""></xref> before the object is reclaimed by garbage collection.
trans-unit.target: Prøver å frigi ressurser ved å kalle <xref uid="langword_csharp_Dispose(false)" name="Dispose(false)" href=""> </xref> før objektet gode av datasanering.

trans-unit.source: This method overrides <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and cleans up resources by calling `Dispose(false)`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden overstyrer <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og rydder opp i ressursene ved å kalle `Dispose(false)`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Override `Dispose(Boolean)` to customize the cleanup.
trans-unit.target: Overstyre `Dispose(Boolean)` tilpasse oppryddingen.

trans-unit.source: Application code should not call this method; an object's `Finalize` method is automatically invoked during garbage collection, unless finalization by the garbage collector has been disabled by a call to the <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Applikasjons-koden kan ikke kalle denne metoden. et objekts `Finalize` metode startes automatisk under datasanering, med mindre finalization av saneringsoppsamlingen er deaktivert av et kall til den <xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.GC.SuppressFinalize%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Finalize Methods and Destructors](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/fd376774-1643-499b-869e-9546a3aeea70), [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [fullføre metoder og destruktører](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/fd376774-1643-499b-869e-9546a3aeea70), [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), og [overstyrer metoden fullføre](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).

trans-unit.source: Attempts to retrieve the specified type of service from the design mode site of the designer's component.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å hente angitte tjenestetype fra utformingen modus området for den utformeren komponent.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of this method requests the service from the site of the component.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av denne metoden forespørsler tjenesten fra området for komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The type of service to request.
trans-unit.target: Tjenestetype å be om.

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the requested service, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the service cannot be resolved.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer tjenesten, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis tjenesten kan ikke løses.

trans-unit.source: Gets an attribute that indicates the type of inheritance of the associated component.
trans-unit.target: Henter et attributt som angir hvilken type arvingen for den tilknyttede komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"></xref> for the associated component.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"> </xref> for den tilknyttede komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether this component is inherited.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om denne komponenten er arvet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the component is inherited; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis komponenten er arvet; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the specified component.
trans-unit.target: Forbereder utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den angitte komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls this method when it is ready to use the designer.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten kaller opp denne metoden når den er klar til å bruke designer.

trans-unit.source: The component for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Komponenten for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Reinitializes an existing component.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en eksisterende komponent.

trans-unit.source: The InitializeExistingComponent method is called when an existing component is being reinitialized.
trans-unit.target: Metoden InitializeExistingComponent kalles når en eksisterende komponent initialiseres.

trans-unit.source: For example, this may occur after the user drags a component to another container.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel kan dette skje når brukeren drar en komponent til en annen beholderen.

trans-unit.source: You may use the `defaultValues` dictionary to apply recommended defaults to properties; however, you should not modify component properties aside from those stored in the dictionary, because this existing component may already have properties set on it.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den `defaultValues` ordlisten å bruke anbefales standarder for, men du bør ikke endre egenskaper for bortsett fra de som er lagret i ordlisten, fordi denne eksisterende komponenten er kanskje allerede egenskaper som er angitt i den.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of this method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av denne metoden støtter ingenting.

trans-unit.source: A name/value dictionary of default values to apply to properties.
trans-unit.target: Et navn/verdi-ordliste for standardverdier for å bruke egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: May be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no default values are specified.
trans-unit.target: Det kan hende <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis ingen standardverdier er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a newly created component.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en nyopprettede komponent.

trans-unit.source: The InitializeNewComponent method is called when a component is first initialized, typically after being first added to a design surface.
trans-unit.target: Metoden InitializeNewComponent kalles når en komponent er initialisert, vanligvis etter først å legge til en utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: You may perform any necessary initialization of this component, and you may ignore the `defaultValues` dictionary altogether.
trans-unit.target: Du kan utføre alle nødvendige initialisering av denne komponenten, og du kan ignorere den `defaultValues` ordlisten helt.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of this method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av denne metoden støtter ingenting.

trans-unit.source: A name/value dictionary of default values to apply to properties.
trans-unit.target: Et navn/verdi-ordliste for standardverdier for å bruke egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: May be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no default values are specified.
trans-unit.target: Det kan hende <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis ingen standardverdier er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the settings for an imported component that is already initialized to settings other than the defaults.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer innstillingene for en importerte komponenten er allerede initialisert innstillinger enn standardinnstillingene.

trans-unit.source: This method is called when the designer is associated with a control that is not in its default state, such as a control that you paste or move with a drag-and-drop operation onto the designer.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles når designer er knyttet til en kontroll som ikke er i standardtilstanden, for eksempel en kontroll som du limer inn, eller Flytt med dra og slipp på designer.

trans-unit.source: This method provides an opportunity for implementers to modify or shadow the properties of the component rather than initialize the properties for the component to their defaults.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden gir mulighet til implementers å endre eller skyggelegge egenskaper for komponenten i stedet initialisere egenskapene for komponenten til standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: This method is called after the other initialization functions.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles etter andre initialisering funksjonene.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"></xref> of the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"> </xref> for det angitte <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref> whose inheritance attribute to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref> der arv attributt som skal hente.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"></xref> of the specified designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.InheritanceAttribute"> </xref> for den angitte utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Sets the default properties for the component.
trans-unit.target: Angir standardegenskapene for komponenten.

trans-unit.source: OnSetComponentDefaults is called when the designer is initialized.
trans-unit.target: OnSetComponentDefaults kalles når designer er initialisert.

trans-unit.source: This allows the designer to provide default values for the base component.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at utformeren for å angi standardverdier for komponenten base.

trans-unit.source: This method is called only once: when you first create the component by dragging it from the Toolbox to the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles én gang: Når du oppretter komponenten dra den fra verktøykassen til utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: Subsequent initializations of the designer do not invoke this method.
trans-unit.target: Etterfølgende initialiseringer av designer ikke aktivere denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of this method sets the default property of the component to the name of the component if the default property is a string and the property is not already set.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av denne metoden egenskapen standard av komponenten til navnet på komponenten hvis egenskapen default er en streng og egenskapen ikke er allerede angitt.

trans-unit.source: This method can be implemented in a derived class to customize the initialization of the component that this designer is designing.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan implementeres i en avledet klasse tilpasse initialisering av komponenten utformeren utformer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent component for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter den overordnede komponenten for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: This property provides a generic mechanism for discovering parent relationships within designers, and is used by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> object's <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ITreeDesigner> interface implementation.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er en generisk metode for å oppdage relasjoner mellom overordnede i utviklere og brukes av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>objektets <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ITreeDesigner>grensesnitt implementering.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ITreeDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: This property should only return `null` when this designer is the root component.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen må bare returnere `null` når utformeren er root-komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The default implementation of this property returns the root component for all components that are not the root component, and it returns `null` for the root component.
trans-unit.target: Standard implementering av denne egenskapen returnerer root-komponenten for alle komponenter som ikke er rotkomponenten, og den `null` for root-komponenten.

trans-unit.source: The parent component for this designer, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if this designer is the root component.
trans-unit.target: Den overordnede komponenten for utformeren, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> hvis utformeren root-komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Allows a designer to change or remove items from the set of attributes that it exposes through a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Tillater en designer til å endre eller fjerne elementer fra settet med attributter som den viser via en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method provides a way to change or remove the items within the dictionary of attributes that are exposed through a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the design-time verbs supported by the component that is associated with the designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter utformingen verbene som støttes av komponenten som er knyttet til designer.

trans-unit.source: This method returns `null` if the component has no design-time verbs.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden returnerer `null` Hvis komponenten har ingen utformingen verb.

trans-unit.source: The design-time environment typically displays verbs returned by this method in a shortcut (right-click) menu.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen miljøet viser vanligvis verb som returneres av denne metoden i en hurtigmeny (Høyreklikk).

trans-unit.source: When a user selects one of the verbs, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A> method of the corresponding <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Når en bruker velger ett av verbene den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A>metoden for den tilsvarende <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb>aktiveres.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand.Invoke%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A design-time environment typically provides a **Properties** command on a component's shortcut menu.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Et utformingen miljø gir vanligvis en **Egenskaper** på hurtigmenyen for en komponent.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, do not include such an entry in the collection of designer-specified verbs.
trans-unit.target: Derfor ikke Inkluder denne oppføring i samlingen av designer angitt verb.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"></xref> of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"></xref> objects, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if no designer verbs are available.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"> </xref> av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"> </xref> objekter, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis det finnes ingen Spørringsutformer verb.
